<p>Set to the iconic Bond theme song, fans are re-introduced to villain Blofeld, played by Christoph Waltz, who sits in a cage in a prison cell.</p>

<p>He tells Bond: 'James, fate draws us back together and now your enemy is my enemy', with the nemesis in question being none other than Safin. </p>

<p>In the trailer, 007 is told of the danger Safin presents by Madeleine Swann, (Lea Seydoux) who tells him that he is after 'revenge' and her, suggesting her life will be in danger if his plans come to pass.  </p>

