<p>British star Lashana Lynch, will be given Bond's licence to kill in the 25th movie in the franchise. She's not the new Bond, but a new character who takes over his secret agent number after he leaves MI6.</p>

<p>Nomi is clearly a force to be reckoned with as Bond refers to her as a 'disarming young woman' after she attempts to shoot him.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Paloma is seen scolding Bond for being late for his meeting with her before she fights off a group of men while wearing a black evening dress.  </p>

<p>Safin appears to see a degree of similarity between himself and 007 as he is overheard eerily proclaiming: 'James Bond, we both eradicate people to try and make the world a better place. I just want to be a little...tidier.' </p>

